  "rating": 2,
  "description": [
    {
      "title": "Volume 1: Genesis",
      "text": "Ordinary people discover they possess extraordinary abilities. As they come to terms with their powers, they must navigate the mysteries surrounding their origins and the looming threat of a catastrophe that could change the world."
    },
    {
      "title": "Volume 2: Generations",
      "text": "The characters continue to explore their powers while new individuals with abilities emerge. A global conspiracy and the hunt for a virus add to the intrigue as the heroes try to prevent a deadly outbreak."
    },
    {
      "title": "Volume 3. Part 1: Villains",
      "text": "The heroes face new challenges as they confront government scrutiny and a malevolent villain, Arthur Petrelli. The discovery of dangerous abilities and a divided group of heroes complicate their mission to save the world from powerful threats."
    },
    {
      "title": "Volume 3. Part 2: Fugitives",
      "text": "The heroes continue their journey, facing government forces and an ever-growing threat. A new organization, Building 26, seeks to control those with abilities, forcing the heroes into a fugitive lifestyle as they strive to protect themselves and others."
    },
    {
      "title": "Volume 4: Redemption",
      "text": "The heroes deals with the carnage caused by a carnival of people with abilities. They must unite to thwart the carnival's leader, Samuel Sullivan, and face their destinies in an epic showdown."
    }
  ],
